    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior, has been meticulously maintained without a single blemish. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as they should, offering a driving experience identical to a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a car in truly exceptional, collector-grade condition.",
