      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle is maintained to a concours-grade standard, exhibiting an immaculate exterior profile and a pristine interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, mirroring its showroom-floor origins. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 46800.0,
